Privacy Policy for ReWear
This Privacy Policy applies to the ReWear app (hereinafter referred to as "Application") for mobile devices created by Ali Yapici (hereinafter referred to as "Service Provider") as a Freemium service. This service is intended for use "AS IS".
Effective Date: January 29, 2025
1. Information Collection and Use
We value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal data in compliance with applicable data protection laws, including the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR), the California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA), and the California Privacy Rights Act (CPRA).
The Application collects and processes personal data that you provide to us, including but not limited to:
Your photos for virtual try-on purposes
Uploaded clothing designs
Try-on history and favorites
Usage statistics and preferences
Device information for optimization
This information is used to:
Provide virtual try-on services
Save your try-on history in your wardrobe
Improve the AI clothing swap technology
Enhance user experience and app performance
Communicate updates and support information
2. Data Sharing and Disclosure
We do not share your personal photos or designs with third parties. All personal data collected is used solely for the purposes described in this Privacy Policy and is processed on secure servers.
3. Automatically Collected Information
We may collect certain information automatically to improve user experience and for analytics purposes, including but not limited to:
Your device's Internet Protocol (IP) address
Device type and operating system
Usage statistics within the Application
Time and date of your use
Performance and error data
4. AI Technology and Image Processing
The Application utilizes artificial intelligence technologies for virtual try-on features. While we strive to ensure high-quality results:
Photos are processed securely using AI technology
We implement NSFW (Not Safe For Work) filters
AI-generated results may vary in quality
We do not store your original photos longer than necessary
You maintain ownership of your photos and designs
5. User Responsibility
You agree not to use the Application to:
Upload inappropriate or offensive content
Violate any third-party clothing design rights
Share or distribute AI-generated results inappropriately
Attempt to bypass our NSFW filters
6. Data Security
We implement strong security measures to protect your photos and personal data, including:
Secure photo processing
Encrypted data transmission
Secure cloud storage
Regular security audits
7. Data Retention
Try-on results are stored in your wardrobe until you delete them
Original photos are deleted after processing
Account data is retained while your account is active
8. Your Rights
Under GDPR, CCPA, and CPRA, you have the right to:
Access your stored data
Delete your try-on history
Request data portability
Opt-out of data collection
Delete your account and associated data
9. Children's Privacy
The Application is not intended for use by anyone under the age of 13. We do not knowingly process photos or collect data from children.
10. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. Users will be notified of significant changes through the Application.
11. Contact Us
For privacy-related questions or concerns:
Email: support@rewear.aliyapici.dev
Website: https://rewear.aliyapici.dev
12. Disclaimer of Warranties
The Application and its AI-generated results are provided "AS IS" without any warranties. Results may vary based on photo quality and clothing selection.
13. Limitation of Liability
We are not liable for:
Unsatisfactory try-on results
Temporary service interruptions
Loss of saved try-ons or favorites
Issues with photo processing or AI generation
By using the Application, you agree to this Privacy Policy and consent to the processing of your data as described above.
Last Updated: January 29, 2025